=== test.177: NVRAM BAR2 write after safe sleep/resetintr — stage=0 ===
Date: Mon Apr 20 18:24:23 BST 2026

Stage 0: skip_arm=1 — download_fw_nvram: enter_download_state (read-only) + BAR2 ioread32 probe + 442KB iowrite32 fw; sleeps 100 ms, reads host resetintr from fw->data, writes NVRAM to BAR2, releases fw/NVRAM, returns -ENODEV.
(test.177: test.176 proved host resetintr extraction after safe msleep(100) survives. This run adds only the NVRAM BAR2 write before release/return. Still no post-write ARM probe, device resetintr use, NVRAM marker readback, TCM dump, or ARM release.)

=== Pre-test BAR0 MMIO guard ===
BAR0 MMIO UR/I/O error (6ms) — device alive; SBR in probe should fix. Proceeding.

